{"word":"H2331 - חָוָה - châvâh - khaw-vah' - Show - காட்டு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>חָוָה"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châvâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-vah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Show / காட்டு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வெளிப்படுத்து, தெரிவி, சொல்லிக்காண்பி, தெரியப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) (Piel) to tell, to declare, to show, to make known"},{"paragraph":"2) to breath"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; (compare <a href=\"#/H2324 - חֲוָא - chăvâʼ - khav-aw'/2324\">H2324</a>, <a href=\"#/H2421 - חָיָה - châyâh - khaw-yaw'/2421\">H2421</a>); properly to <i>live</i>; by implication (intensively) to <i>declare</i> or <i>show: - </i>show."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2331 - חָוָה - châvâh - khaw-vah'/2331\">H2331</a>, <a href=\"#/H262 - אַחְוָה - ʼachvâh - akh-vaw'/262\">H262</a>"}]}